Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: First woman Supreme Court judge
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wjkd
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Sep 1981
Reagan appointment Sandra Day O'Connor confirmed as first woman judge to Supreme Court panel. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less